{"tid":416262,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"仲記唔記得當年高登幾多巴打俾警犬拉？連登有無？","createTime":"2017-09-27T15:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T06:55:12.000Z","uid":38795,"like":41,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d3752a5f60edd8650dae7257284981aca5f35f9c","tid":416262,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:46:33.000Z","msg":"記得之前有巴打爆料話警犬要早洩俾資料早洩二話不說就俾左，結果經常見到有巴打係網上講句野就不誠實使用電腦，因為早洩根本對你WFC<br />\n<br />\n連登開左咁耐有無巴打俾警犬拉？<br />\n<br />\n話要拉大隊返高登嗰d返左去既話唔好怨點解又有巴打俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f428a7b352f192f89865b4f3b341cf9e6bc755","tid":416262,"uid":2295,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:48:42.000Z","msg":"由鳩班契弟興風作浪<br />\n佢地無野做 得閒得濟 <br />\n唔好理 當睇唔到咪算"},{"pid":"0c82ccfed70dadb6ccf77f216a722ff6c23371a2","tid":416262,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:51:57.000Z","msg":"實捉到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4092637303a68fd37c30f8432a522fcbb66d40","tid":416262,"uid":86962,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講得啱！高登打手必定無視<br />\n<br />\n當年宣傳連登俾人大屠殺<br />\n呢到日日叫人回老家都無俾人ban <br />\n<br />\n當初唔理會員意見，e 家見人走哂就扮死狗，派打手過黎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">高下立見</span></span>"},{"pid":"13af4113783df25851b8daefa53626f741d73650","tid":416262,"uid":145451,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T22:43:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37b418229375aaa8912653b30a48563b2b951a67","tid":416262,"uid":77164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T22:46:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"940894eb3fa9871eef8cf3b8e8e2da5e037f7b61","tid":416262,"uid":13466,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T23:35:06.000Z","msg":"其實我真係唔明喺d「回家post」入面，d人講咁多做乜鳩？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/072941_3a4335dadff75f22089e22eb54c9ce8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F072941_3a4335dadff75f22089e22eb54c9ce8a.jpg&h=5513d135&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/072942_6d6b85df26cf9f22cc9e183f6cce510d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F072942_6d6b85df26cf9f22cc9e183f6cce510d.jpg&h=44c63250&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n淨係講早洩到而家都仲係iproA常務理事，係同葛珮帆、團結香港基金班友係一丘之貉，就已經知個forum去唔過啦！<br />\n<br />\n呢d forum，隨時一個唔該開個「若蓮喪子post」都比早洩交人出去告不誠實使用電腦呀！<br />\n<br />\n話連尼住會刪post所以要回家嗰d，咁你可以連連登都唔上架，唔上forum唔會死的，咁都推論到要回家嘅話，一係邏輯混亂、一係打手。"},{"pid":"124a700e40a635301d7d49cd997b38e83aebcea3","tid":416262,"uid":145451,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T23:40:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a31c09744d235995d5398d76e7fa0e46b4b22162","tid":416262,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T23:45:08.000Z","msg":"高登十年以上<br />\n連登一年都冇<br />\n同埋暫時唔見連登有咩值得俾人拉既post"},{"pid":"37d5ae9def1ca82a0c817c662f00add1c69c7f53","tid":416262,"uid":145451,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T23:47:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3872b0d58457b5bc05a32b0caceae2ba43c58b8","tid":416262,"uid":145451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T23:49:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b6ff253afeda8b3b17f8d633d06fd0e8254722e","tid":416262,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T00:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8122b9c425fa0f03d46e4e64120601ac5810ac83","tid":416262,"uid":24282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講陰